=== Tasuddest tagensawt ===
Yeṭra i mezweɣ ayen yetran i tegnit seg [[tamagarda tamtiwgant|tmagarda tamtiwgant]], tamagarda dagi d tamhelt i d-ittfarasen amgirred deg tneẓẓi d isegran n yal tissi n tiddiwin n umtiweg, anda ul n umtiweg yettili tneẓẓi-ines teflal ma d ayen i d-izgan dennig-s tineẓẓi-ines tettili ddaw n tneẓẓi n wul.<ref>Nimmo, Francis; Tanaka, Ken (2005). "Early Crustal Evolution of Mars". Annual Review of Earth and Planetary Sciences. 33 (1): 133–161. Bibcode:2005AREPS..33..133N. doi:10.1146/annurev.earth.33.092203.122637.</ref>

== [[Adad agnaw|Adad agennaw]] ==

== [[Anezwu]] ==
Gar n [[itrikli|yimtiwgen]] n [[udus anafuk|wudus anafuk]] yakk, [[tasemhuyt|tisemhuyin]] n mezweɣ yettemcabin s waṭas i tsemhuyin n tegnit, s usrag n wannuz yemgadan n [[Agellus n tuzzya|ugellus n tuzzya n sin n imtiwegen-a]]. Tanzagt n tsemhuyin n mezweɣ gdant snat n tikkal n tenzagt n tsemhuyin n tegnit acku amaccaq n mezweɣ ɣer tfukt yugar amaccaq n tegnit ɣer tfukt (yiwet n tuzzya n tegnit ɣef tfukt, tettqabal-itt snat n tuzzyiwin n mezweɣ ɣef tfukt). Dɣa [[taẓɣelt]] deg mezweɣ temgarad seg izaduren anda tettili -143 C (-225 F) deg [[Tagrest|tegrest]] tasafaylut<ref>"What is the typical temperature on Mars?". Astronomycafe.net. Retrieved August 14, 2012.</ref> alamma d yiswiren anda tettawaṭ ɣer 35 C (95 F) deg [[anebdu|unebdu]] asbegsan.<ref>"Mars Exploration Rover Mission: Spotlight". Marsrover.nasa.gov. June 12, 2007. Retrieved August 14, 2012.</ref>

Amgarad hrawen deg tezɣelt yettuɣal usrag-is (sebba-ines) ɣer [[adad agnaw|wadad agennaw]] usdid ur nezmir ara ad iffren aṭas seg teẓɣelt n tfukt d waẓaẓ drusen n wakal n mezweɣ.<ref name="m.a37">"Mars' desert surface..." MGCM Press release. NASA. Archived from the original on July 7, 2007. Retrieved February 25, 2007.</ref> mezweɣ yaggug (yebɛed) 1,52 n tikkal ɣef tfukt seg wala [[tagnit]], ayen i s-d-itfarasen 43% kan n tesmekta n tafat n tfukt.<ref name="a m77">Kluger, Jeffrey (September 1, 1992). "Mars, in Earth's Image". Discover Magazine. 13 (9): 70. Bibcode:1992Disc...13...70K. Retrieved November 3, 2009.</ref>

Awah tmezzit yecban agla n tegnit i mezweɣ, tili tisemhuyin-is ad ilint am wagla n tegnit acku annuz-is agellusan yemmug am tmezzit n tegnit.

Llan deg mezweɣ iluɣluɣen (aṭu n wakal) imeqqren yakk deg [[udus anafuk|wudus anafuk]], anda tettawaṭ tazzla-ines ar ugar n 160 km/[[tasragt|t]]. Zemren ad mgaraden seg iluɣluɣen deg tjumma meẓẓiyen alamma d iluɣluɣen icafcalen i zemren ad ffren amtiweg s timmad-is. iluɣluɣen-a ttmagen-d aladɣa mi ara ad yades (ad iqerreb) ɣer tfukt .<ref name="a m76">Philips, Tony (July 16, 2001). "Planet Gobbling Dust Storms". Science @ NASA. Archived from the original on June 13, 2006. Retrieved June 7, 2006.</ref>

